WEBVTT

00:01:48.720 --> 00:01:52.469
Well, good afternoon family.

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:55.109
Thank you for joining me again today. We

00:01:55.109 --> 00:01:55.119
are

00:01:55.119 --> 00:01:57.030
going to go over some things

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:59.030
