00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:31.110
believe many hands make light work.

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:33.430
And I have been asked a lot lately,

00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:35.670
Brandon, do you call yourself a prophet?

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:38.550
I just call myself Brandon Biggs. I call

00:02:38.560 --> 00:02:41.270
