00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:44.309
said, Raise up a million-man

00:02:44.309 --> 00:02:44.319
and woman

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:47.589
prayer army. And in doing so,

00:02:47.599 --> 00:02:49.910
we will pray and we will change the

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.470
nations through prayer. And I truly

00:02:52.480 --> 00:02:55.350
believe, like I said, many hands make

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:56.710
light work. But you have to have a

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.470
leader. And the Lord said,

00:02:58.480 --> 00:03:00.390
Lead the people. Teach them how to

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.750
