00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.869
And so, I am excited that you all

00:03:06.879 --> 00:03:08.790
take it seriously. I am excited that every

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.070
single one of you would want to pray

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:14.070
with me and do the things that we do. It

00:03:14.070 --> 00:03:14.080
is

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:16.949
not easy, pressing in and

00:03:16.959 --> 00:03:19.910
praying and

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:22.550
you know, through the trenches

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.830
basically is what I want to call it. But

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:27.670
you know, I am grateful for every

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:30.550
single one of you that pray. And so I

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.470
believe

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:34.630
everything the Lord has showed me in my

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.430
opinion is by the spirit, by the

00:03:37.430 --> 00:03:37.440
unction

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.350
