02:52:53.040 --> 02:52:55.830
Father, we just thank You for

02:52:55.840 --> 02:52:58.070
the souls.

02:52:58.080 --> 02:52:59.590
We thank You, Father, for the born

02:52:59.600 --> 02:53:01.269
again.

02:53:01.279 --> 02:53:03.429
Now, Father, we call for our unsaved

02:53:03.439 --> 02:53:05.670
loved ones before we close tonight. We

02:53:05.680 --> 02:53:08.309
thank You, Lord. We call every single

02:53:08.319 --> 02:53:10.309
one of them born again. The Bible says

02:53:10.319 --> 02:53:12.550
that Satan has blinded the eyes of the

02:53:12.560 --> 02:53:15.269
unbeliever. And we call the unbelieving

02:53:15.279 --> 02:53:18.389
eyes to believe in the name of Jesus. We

02:53:18.399 --> 02:53:21.269
call the enlightenment of the eyes. We

02:53:21.279 --> 02:53:24.389
say according to Ephesians

02:53:24.399 --> 02:53:26.309
that the eyes of their understanding

02:53:26.319 --> 02:53:28.389
would be enlightened tonight. We say,

02:53:28.399 --> 02:53:30.870
'Satan, get your hands off of our unsaved

02:53:30.880 --> 02:53:34.070
loved ones.'We call them born again. We

02:53:34.070 --> 02:53:34.080
call

02:53:34.080 --> 02:53:36.469
them baptized in the Holy Ghost

02:53:36.479 --> 02:53:39.269
on fire for Jesus and they will be a

02:53:39.279 --> 02:53:42.230
light to the world. And Father, I thank

02:53:42.240 --> 02:53:44.070
you, Lord.

02:53:44.080 --> 02:53:47.030
We thank you, Lord, that tonight we arise

02:53:47.040 --> 02:53:48.950
and shine, for the light has come and the

02:53:48.960 --> 02:53:51.269
glory of the Lord has risen on us, and we

02:53:51.279 --> 02:53:52.790
give you all the glory, honor, and praise

02:53:52.800 --> 02:53:55.590
for it, Lord, in the name of Jesus.

02:53:55.600 --> 02:53:59.349
Everyone say, 'Amen and amen.'So I kept

02:53:59.359 --> 02:54:01.910
you about three hours. I'm so thankful

02:54:01.920 --> 02:54:03.670
for every single one of you that

02:54:03.670 --> 02:54:03.680
came

02:54:03.680 --> 02:54:05.510
out tonight and prayed with us. How many

02:54:05.520 --> 02:54:09.269
do we have all together?

02:54:09.279 --> 02:54:10.230
Seven.

02:54:10.240 --> 02:54:12.150
Well, we came on earlier and still have a good

02:54:12.160 --> 02:54:14.950
crowd. So, all 7,000 of you, thank you

02:54:14.960 --> 02:54:16.550
for being here. We're really

02:54:16.560 --> 02:54:18.790
appreciative of it. We'll

02:54:18.800 --> 02:54:21.110
be back again tomorrow. Do you like

02:54:21.120 --> 02:54:22.950
the new time? We tried a

02:54:22.960 --> 02:54:24.710
little bit earlier. Usually, we come on

02:54:24.720 --> 02:54:27.110
about 9:00, somewhere around there. So,

02:54:27.120 --> 02:54:28.469
we tried something a little different

02:54:28.479 --> 02:54:30.230
tonight. So, if you like this time

02:54:30.240 --> 02:54:32.309
frame, let us know. We're trying to do

02:54:32.319 --> 02:54:33.830
something different. I get tired of

02:54:33.840 --> 02:54:36.070
getting in a rut and doing the same

02:54:36.080 --> 02:54:38.150
thing over and over again. And so,

02:54:38.160 --> 02:54:39.510
that's what we're doing

02:54:39.510 --> 02:54:39.520
differently

02:54:39.520 --> 02:54:42.309
tonight. So to those that are used to

02:54:42.319 --> 02:54:44.550
coming on at 9:00, you can watch the

02:54:44.560 --> 02:54:47.830
replay. So God bless you all. We close

02:54:47.840 --> 02:54:49.830
by saying this: We love you. Thank you

02:54:49.840 --> 02:54:51.269
for your support. Thank you for praying

02:54:51.279 --> 02:54:53.269
for my family. We appreciate every

02:54:53.279 --> 02:54:55.349
single one of you. And we are so excited

02:54:55.359 --> 02:54:57.590
that you pray with us. And we will

02:54:57.600 --> 02:54:59.990
see you again. Remember, put a smile on

02:55:00.000 --> 02:55:03.030
your face and a song in your heart.

02:55:03.040 --> 02:55:05.110
Jesus loves you so much and we love you.

02:55:05.120 --> 02:55:06.630
God bless you and we'll see you again. Bye-bye.

